                            d="M100.41 53.48C75.61 53.48 55.42 33.3 55.42 8.48999H32.99C32.99 25.76 39.52 41.52 50.24 53.48H0.0100098V75.91H50.22C39.52 87.84 33 103.63 33 120.9H55.43C55.43 96.1 75.61 75.91 100.42 75.91V53.48H100.41Z"
